Third-party FFmpegKit / FFmpeg notice
-------------------------------------

NovaCut may bundle `com.moizhassan.ffmpeg:ffmpeg-kit-16kb:6.1.1` for
FFmpeg-backed export paths that AndroidX Media3 Transformer does not cover.
The resolved Maven POM declares LGPL-3.0, while the packaged AAR includes
GPLv3 license text and a GPLv3 source-offer resource. Treat redistributed
NovaCut builds that include this AAR as carrying FFmpegKit / FFmpeg GPLv3
notice and source-offer obligations unless the dependency is replaced by a
verified LGPL-only build flavor.

The Android package includes FFmpegKit's upstream license resources under
`res/raw/license*.txt` and `res/raw/source.txt`. Keep those resources in any
redistributed build, and provide source access or a written source offer for
the FFmpegKit / FFmpeg components according to those bundled terms.
